                      "y": 0,
                      "name": "para2Text",
                      "fill": "#C8C8C8",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 680,
                      "content": "\"You came.\" Damien's voice was low, a rumble that vibrated through the empty hall. He emerged from the shadows near the grand staircase, his dark suit absorbing what little light remained. His jaw was set, but his eyes — those treacherous eyes — betrayed something she'd never seen in them before. Vulnerability.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.85,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
