                  "name": "t1txt",
                  "fill": "#848484",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I've never read AI-generated prose this good. The enemies-to-lovers story had me screaming at 2 AM. The tension, the dialogue — it felt like a real novel.",
